{"tid":2143563,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街家品店遭淋紅油 負責人稱閉路電視已拍下經過","createTime":"2020-08-07T07:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T17:11:08.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3782d8f9e05572663dbde02e20737db16df24241","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200806/s00001/8dd9611c0bad510c68c9526ea3929437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200806%2Fs00001%2F8dd9611c0bad510c68c9526ea3929437.jpg&h=978654a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200806/s00001/8dd95176fb22b873357d7629f6e8a4fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200806%2Fs00001%2F8dd95176fb22b873357d7629f6e8a4fe.jpg&h=e71b1b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨約4時半，觀塘瑞和街33號一間家品店門外大閘遭淋紅油，警員接報到場並通知負責人返店協助調查。負責人稱店外閉路電視已拍下案發經過，又稱沒有與人結怨，不清楚被淋油原因。"},{"pid":"d217fa6d5ab4d5c59b336e1c8d07f75d031148ba","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"瑞和街街市男子拒戴口罩  食環署首次按599I提出檢控<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2127920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2127920</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街海味店遇竊 失8000元花膠<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1971955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1971955</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街糧食店被罰暫停營業十四天<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697001</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘瑞和街七人車冒煙起火 消防開喉灌救<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011649</a><br />\n<br />\n22歲邱東觀塘瑞和街失蹤 警籲提供消息<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fsyisS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fsyisS</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣髮廊掠四萬 瑞和街殘廁分贓 三青年獲輕判<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1825492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1825492</a><br />\n<br />\n26歲男瑞和街電競中心傷人 判監30個月 (案件編號：DCCC 142/2018)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n瑞和街綜援白卡婦襲擊圖書館職員 上訴失敗判處入獄4星期<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845986</a><br />\n<br />\n14歲少年向女友發跳海尋死短訊  竟於瑞和街尋回<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eKKsfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eKKsfS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街掃違例泊車 揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1186592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1186592</a>"},{"pid":"9627ffd31431eed6a9bc65017171422a0d989053","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"●街市/市政大廈●曾到訪患者數字●<br />\n●九龍區<br />\n●深水埗北河街街市及熟食中心/北河街市政大廈●22人<br />\n●紅磡街市/紅磡市政大廈 ●21人<br />\n●黃大仙大成街街市●10人<br />\n●牛池灣市政大廈●15人<br />\n●土瓜灣市政大廈暨政府合署●11人<br />\n●觀塘瑞和街市政大廈●9人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c43cd87f172cc7f601a5b8f2ff2d9e4ee29373f","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200805/photo/bkn-20200805210350531-0805_00822_001_08b.jpg?20200805220422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200805%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200805210350531-0805_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20200805220422&h=1a56d77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於觀塘瑞和街街市亦有老鼠出沒，雖然食環署清潔工人於街市內清潔，但仍有不少老鼠在街市外圍伺機而動，四出覓食。"},{"pid":"3f1c2022d850b8818b685fb8e85a4ee29474f9b4","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200805/photo/bkn-20200805115613480-0805_00822_001_09b.jpg?20200806041615\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200805%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200805115613480-0805_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20200806041615&h=2e189fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘瑞和街街市情況惡劣，街市通風設備亦不佳，有不少蔬菜及垃圾棄置在地面，食物殘渣成老鼠天堂。菜檔檔主劉小姐指，每日都能看見如手掌大小老鼠四處走，今早還有老鼠死在蔬菜上，情況每個月也會出現三至四次。"},{"pid":"9715a1134f7ac9e50045c114b1f0d46a621c8421","tid":2143563,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c43cd87f172cc7f601a5b8f2ff2d9e4ee29373f","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200805/photo/bkn-20200805210350531-0805_00822_001_08b.jpg?20200805220422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200805%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200805210350531-0805_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20200805220422&h=1a56d77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於觀塘瑞和街街市亦有老鼠出沒，雖然食環署清潔工人於街市內清潔，但仍有不少老鼠在街市外圍伺機而動，四出覓食。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8561d682afeb415f240377751014aeab2703bc","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"<em> 民政總署上月已經與東華三院合作推出「慈雲山檢測計劃」。由明日開始，2019冠狀病毒病免費檢測計劃範圍將陸續擴大，包括黃大仙區慈愛苑；[url]觀塘區彩福邨、坪石邨、啟業邨、彩霞邨[/url]；屯門區山景邨、蝴蝶邨；和油尖旺區創德樓、中原樓，共涵蓋46座樓宇，約86 000名居民。<br />\n2020年8月6日（星期四）</em>"},{"pid":"486e229526dd56b1bb4814a12064aad5cf776b1b","tid":2143563,"uid":200882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"其實係宇狗嘅血 世清好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d1ed7b241d8cdd3c96fcf1c145ca8e61a97528","tid":2143563,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"486e229526dd56b1bb4814a12064aad5cf776b1b","tid":2143563,"uid":200882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:21:04.000Z